{"tid":466182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁愛詩：國歌法可設追溯期","createTime":"2017-11-12T10:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T15:14:04.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4f6cfb6b6f5665bd8d396c50d03a1ed76ab009","tid":466182,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"《國歌法》暫未在港進行本地立法，對於日前再有球迷噓國歌，基本法委員會副主任、前律政司司長梁愛詩不希望有人利用這段空檔再侮辱國家，她相信立法會有權為《國歌法》設追溯期。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩表示，《國歌法》不應該有追溯力，而香港一般刑法也無追溯力，但過往亦曾有設追溯力的本港法律。她認為，在《國歌法》本地立法前，一旦出現大規模侮辱國歌行為而且影響社會，立法會可視乎情況，在通過草案時列明《國歌法》在立法前何時生效。"},{"pid":"28ce5128f441193a220830e94d1ae49badcbbf04","tid":466182,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"特區妖婦"},{"pid":"46858fcc0e764e67204b04b93e2549a1ecd292a3","tid":466182,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"講到明唔可以侮辱，你哋繼續怪邊個"},{"pid":"1cfa923548291278207403c4f66b3ce88a00e875","tid":466182,"uid":2446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到明唔可以侮辱，你哋繼續怪邊個</blockquote><br />\n發現"},{"pid":"37432f56a30217c529770f268acc29c1f02be634","tid":466182,"uid":19676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"點解咁耐條仆街都未死？"},{"pid":"7a3225ee735737c69021f18563f106374b052501","tid":466182,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"慘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0C4xrwke03w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0C4xrwke03w&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=117cd5ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0C4xrwke03w</a>"},{"pid":"013c208712eeab8efe87a9ac6e21ab60876455fb","tid":466182,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"立法會係可以設追溯期，但上到法庭一定會被判違憲。"},{"pid":"f7bf5c68cbc2b7e7be112a60f6b7d864cc69b416","tid":4